ise of a profitable ethics review industry.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aBureaucracyzUnited States. 0aHuman experimentation in medicinexLaw and legislationzUnited States. 0aInstitutional review boards (Medicine)zUnited States. 0aMedical ethics committeeszUnited States. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aInstitutional Review Boards (IRBs).  abureaucracy.  acompliance.  adelegated governance.  aorganizations.  aprofessions.  aregulation.  awork.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2020 Englishz978311070472308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology, Education, Psychology 2020z9783110704549oZDB-23-SEW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP Frontlist eBook-Package 2020z978311069218140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150361123840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781503611238423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781503611238.jpg  a978-3-11-069218-1  SUP Frontlist eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070472-3  EBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2020 Englishb2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-SEWb2020